info.name: KMS Prinz Heinrich, Prinz Adalbert (Azur Lane)
info.description:
A background of the Roblox website featuring KMS Prinz Heinrich and Prinz Adalbert (left to right) from the mobile videogame Azur Lane.

Do note that the homepage in the screenshot was made possible in conjunction with RoGold, a third-party extension for Roblox that I am not affiliated with.
